{"tid":2184825,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：有無三權分立的爭拗「有點無謂」","createTime":"2020-09-02T00:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T03:42:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f367f98e9dafc4705c7d802f654f668835693d9d","tid":2184825,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊指，本港有無「三權分立」的爭拗有點無謂。他解釋，在基本法下，本港內部治權的政治概念上，有某程度分隔和互相制衡，但憲制安排上沒有三權分立。湯家驊在一個電台節目上指，本港不會因為行政長官林鄭月娥說沒有三權分立，而一夜間失去權力分隔；也不會因為法律界議員郭榮鏗說有三權分立，而改變憲制秩序，認為爭拗無謂。他指，本港有三權分工，亦有互相制衡，而回歸以來權力亦能達至互相制衡的效果。 <br />\n<br />\n湯家驊相信，現時本港處於獨立思想醞釀的敏感時刻，中央政府認為討論獨立政體的「三權分立」並不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2355292&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYSQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=94d9452a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355292</a>"},{"pid":"324e2a68546f5e36c5ba93d8828b6f011d814b06","tid":2184825,"uid":200343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"早晨君君<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bebd6042eca68987a200bf62311ce22d6f6b443","tid":2184825,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:51.000Z","msg":"對11哥嚟講爭拗一個女仔係咪唔夠秤的確「有點無謂」嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw醫生早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb731a0d1803fd55cba9a0ad2d1c62b10fbef4a","tid":2184825,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"324e2a68546f5e36c5ba93d8828b6f011d814b06","tid":2184825,"uid":200343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"早晨君君<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit